snippet.title: Village Monsters Trailer (2019)
snippet.description:
WISHLIST: https://store.steampowered.com/app/679830/Village_Monsters/

FOLLOW: https://twitter.com/VillageMonsters

Village Monsters is an open-ended village life sim set in the world of a long-forgotten video game. You play as a human living in a community of (mostly) friendly monsters.

Live a different kind of life in a different kind of world.

Music - Untitled by Josh Woodward. Free download: http://joshwoodward.com/
